    <solution><p>SOLUTION</p>
<p><me>\begin{array}{rcl} \displaystyle \int_0^{2} (4 e^x+2 \sin x)\, dx \amp =\amp   
\displaystyle  4 e^x-2 \cos x  \Big]_0^{2}
\\ \amp =\amp  (4 e^{2} - 2 \cos 2) - (4 e^0 - 2 \cos0 ) 
\\ \amp =\amp  4 e^{2} - 2 \cos 2 - 2 
\end{array}</me></p>
</solution>
